1
00:00:05,361 --> 00:00:06,580
Murakaza neza nanone.

2
00:00:06,580 --> 00:00:09,783
Muri aka gace tugiye kuvuga
kubyerekeye umutungo kamere.

3
00:00:10,487 --> 00:00:12,067
Tugiye kuwusobanura, tunawuganireho.

4
00:00:12,067 --> 00:00:13,915
Tugiye gushaka ukuntu
utandukanye

5
00:00:13,915 --> 00:00:18,182
n' ubundi bwoko bw' imitungu
n' impamvu amaguverunoma kwisi

6
00:00:18,182 --> 00:00:20,984
uwuzi, uwukoresha, kandi abona ko ari ingenzi

7
00:00:20,984 --> 00:00:24,158
kubantu mu
bihugu byabo ndetse no muboyobozi.

8
00:00:24,765 --> 00:00:28,205
Tugiye kuganira kucyo bishatse kuvuga
mu gihe umuntu akwiganye

9
00:00:28,205 --> 00:00:30,480
ndetse n' uburyo wakwirinda ko
bakwigana.

10
00:00:30,891 --> 00:00:34,467
Nyuma yaho turaza kuvuga birambuye
ku bwoko butandukanye bw'

11
00:00:34,467 --> 00:00:38,275
umutungo kamere,
uhereye kumabanga y' ubucuruzi,

12
00:00:38,275 --> 00:00:42,046
izina, icyemezo cya nyiri sosiyete, uburenganzira bw' umuhanzi

13
00:00:42,046 --> 00:00:45,817
nyuma yaho hari ubundi bwoko bwinshi,
tutaza kuganiraho uyu munsi.

14
00:00:45,817 --> 00:00:47,966
Ebyiri murizo zerekenye kumwambaro y' ubucuruzi,

15
00:00:47,966 --> 00:00:51,548
itandukanya bitewe na reta
kuri reta.

16
00:00:53,078 --> 00:00:54,146
Imitunganyirize.

17
00:00:55,112 --> 00:01:01,027
Ikaba mubyukuri ari kibazo
kuva mugihungu kukindi

18
00:01:01,379 --> 00:01:05,870
Mubyukuri biragoranye cyane--
urabone tuzavuga kumwitunganyirize muri

19
00:01:05,870 --> 00:01:07,519
wenda imwe muyindi nuyu munsi

20
00:01:07,519 --> 00:01:12,323
ariko ntago tuza kubona igihe
cyo kujya byimbitse kubyerekenye imwitunganirize.

21
00:01:12,784 --> 00:01:15,122
Wazabireba kubwawe
kubw' igihugu cyawe.

22
00:01:15,122 --> 00:01:17,789
ukareba uburyo babifatamo
kandi hari ubundi bwoko

23
00:01:17,789 --> 00:01:20,345
bwinshi bwizindi, tutaza kuvugaho uyu munsi.

24
00:01:20,345 --> 00:01:23,025
Turaza kuvuga kubwoko bune bwingenzi
bw' umutungo kamere.

25
00:01:23,290 --> 00:01:24,613
Bityo reka dukomeze.

26
00:01:24,613 --> 00:01:27,684
BItyo reka tuvuge k'umutungo nyawe
ugereranyije n' umutungo wamuntu

27
00:01:27,684 --> 00:01:29,425
ugereranyije n' umutungo kamere

28
00:01:30,192 --> 00:01:34,386
Umutungo nyawe ni umutungo ufatika

29
00:01:34,386 --> 00:01:36,814
utakwimurwa.

30
00:01:37,619 --> 00:01:42,146
Hari ubwoko butandukanye bw' amategeko buza
gutandukanya imitungo

31
00:01:42,146 --> 00:01:44,908
utimurwa ndetse
niya kwimurwa,

32
00:01:44,908 --> 00:01:46,672
Ariwo mutungu w' umuntu.

33
00:01:46,672 --> 00:01:51,145
Urugero rw' imitungo itimurwa:
Inzu yawe, aho uba,

34
00:01:51,145 --> 00:01:55,418
Niba ufite ubutaka-- kugira ngo
ubwohereza hari

35
00:01:55,418 --> 00:01:59,049
amategeko n' amabwirizwa menshi,
wenda n' imisoro

36
00:01:59,049 --> 00:02:04,525
hashobora kuba amategeko menshi yerekeranye
n' ukuntu wagurisha ubutaka bwawe

37
00:02:04,525 --> 00:02:07,448
kuwundi muntu nukuntu yabugura,
n' igihe bashobora

38
00:02:07,448 --> 00:02:08,900
kuyandikaho ahantu, ndetse nibindi.

39
00:02:08,900 --> 00:02:12,451
Mubwiyo mpamvu umutungo utimurwa ufite
amategeko yawu.

40
00:02:12,451 --> 00:02:16,317
Umutungo wawe ni nkindi mitungo
uba ufite

41
00:02:16,317 --> 00:02:20,531
ariko ikaba yakwimukanywa:
nkimyenda yawe, igare ryawe

42
00:02:20,531 --> 00:02:24,167
ndetse nibundi bwoko bw' imitungo yawe

43
00:02:24,167 --> 00:02:28,039
ufite kandi mubyukuri dufite amategeko
n' amabwirizwa yerekeranye nicyo gukora

44
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:29,373
n' umutungo w' umuntu.

45
00:02:29,373 --> 00:02:32,744
Ntukwiye gufata imyambaro y' undi
nta ruhushya

46
00:02:32,744 --> 00:02:34,226
ngo maze utangire kuyambara

47
00:02:34,226 --> 00:02:35,857
Ntabwo wakwiba igare ry'undi.

48
00:02:35,857 --> 00:02:39,056
Uramutse ubikoze wagirana
ibibazo n'amategeko, n'ibindi.

49
00:02:39,056 --> 00:02:42,082
Bitwo umutungo bwite
ni ikintu gifatika.

50
00:02:42,082 --> 00:02:45,575
Noneho ku rundi ruhande,
umutungo w'ubwenge ufatwa nk'

51
00:02:45,575 --> 00:02:49,999
umusaruro w'ubuhanga cyangwa
umusaruro w'imitekerereze.

52
00:02:50,593 --> 00:02:57,679
Ibyo rero ni ibintu nk'ubuvumbuzi,
ubuhimbyi, ubwanditsi, umuziki,

53
00:02:58,313 --> 00:03:04,417
kandi mu binyejana byinshi
hazamutse urusange rw'amategeko

54
00:03:04,417 --> 00:03:09,332
ajyanye no kurema, gutanga,
kugurisha, gukodesha, n'ibindi,

55
00:03:09,332 --> 00:03:11,412
uyu mutungo turi kuvuga hano

56
00:03:11,412 --> 00:03:12,954
kandi ibyo ni byo tugiye
kuganiraho uyu munsi.

57
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:16,823
Reka turebe impamvu ibihugu bitandukanye

58
00:03:16,961 --> 00:03:19,584
byemera umutungo w'ubwenge.

59
00:03:19,748 --> 00:03:22,536
Kuki bishyiraho aya mategeko adasanzwe
agenga umutungo w'ubwenge?

60
00:03:22,747 --> 00:03:27,611
Ibihugu ndetse n'uduce twinshi
bifite amategeko anyuranye mo gato.

61
00:03:28,561 --> 00:03:31,524
Bigenda bigabanyuka uko iminsi ishira

62
00:03:31,524 --> 00:03:38,596
ariko haracyariho amatandukaniro agaragara
hagati y'ibihugu kandi usanza akenshi

63
00:03:38,596 --> 00:03:41,858
ajyanye n'imitekerereze y'

64
00:03:41,858 --> 00:03:44,851
intengo z'uwo mutungo kamere.

65
00:03:45,041 --> 00:03:50,540
Intengo y'umutungo kamere ni
uguha abantu ibibatera ubushake

66
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:54,705
bwo gukora ubuvumbuzi n'ibikorwa by'ubuhanga.

67
00:03:55,649 --> 00:04:01,277
Bityo rero uburyo utangamo ubwo bushake
kuri nyir'uguhimba

68
00:04:01,277 --> 00:04:05,435
cyangwa wa muntu ufite ubuhanga
ubigereranyije n'inyungu za rubanda

69
00:04:05,435 --> 00:04:09,542
bishobora kugira uruhare k'ukuntu
ukora amategeko yawe

70
00:04:09,542 --> 00:04:13,861
ndetse n'amabwiriza ajyanye
n'umutungo kamere w'ubwenge.

71
00:04:13,861 --> 00:04:16,544
Bamwe babyita
"Sisiteme y'igihugu yo guhimba udushya".

72
00:04:16,784 --> 00:04:19,305
Uburyo wubakamo iyo sisiteme
y'igihugu yo guhimba udushya

73
00:04:19,305 --> 00:04:22,121
buterwa n'imyumvire yawe kuri
ibi bintu bitandukanye.

74
00:04:22,121 --> 00:04:26,061
Akenshi usanga hari amategeko
agena guhishura.

75
00:04:26,792 --> 00:04:33,640
Hari umwihariko ndetse
n'uburinzi uba ufite.

76
00:04:33,977 --> 00:04:37,138
Hano guhishura bivuga gusa urungano
rw'amakuru uba ugomba gutanga.

77
00:04:37,302 --> 00:04:44,227
Naho umwihariko bivuga urungano
rw'amakuru wagumana wowe ubwawe

78
00:04:44,384 --> 00:04:46,144
kugirango urinde abandi kukwigana

79
00:04:46,786 --> 00:04:52,926
naho ikiciro ni urungano rw'igihe
uba ufite umwihariko iyo uwufite

80
00:04:52,926 --> 00:04:56,695
kandi ama guverinoma cyangwa za leta

81
00:04:56,695 --> 00:05:02,070
nk'uko tuzita, zavuga ko
hari uguhuriramo hano,

82
00:05:02,212 --> 00:05:07,554
ibyo bintu bitatu bigena imiterere
itandukanye y'ingano y'uko ushaka

83
00:05:07,554 --> 00:05:10,699
kurinda rubanda ndetse n'uko ushaka
kurinda umuntu ku giti cye

84
00:05:10,699 --> 00:05:12,931
mu bijyanye n'umuhimbyi.

85
00:05:13,084 --> 00:05:16,548
Rero nk'ibyiciro birebire, ni urugero,
bifatwa akenshi

86
00:05:16,548 --> 00:05:20,553
nk'ibyungukira cyane umuhimbyi
cyangwa ba bantu bahimba

87
00:05:20,553 --> 00:05:25,339
kubera ko biborohereza gukura amafaranga
mu bihangano cyangwa ubuvumbuzi bwabo.

88
00:05:26,921 --> 00:05:30,842
Ku rundi ruhande, ntabwo ibyo ari byiza
cyane kuri rubanda kuko bitwara igihe kinini cyane

89
00:05:30,842 --> 00:05:33,672
mbere y'uko watangira kubakira
kuri bya bihangano bya mbere

90
00:05:33,803 --> 00:05:40,739
mu gihe ibyiciro bigufi byo kwikubira
biganisha ahari ku nyungu ya rubanda

91
00:05:40,739 --> 00:05:43,790
nubwo bamwe bashobora kubihakana
ariko bishobora kwangiza iterabushake

92
00:05:43,790 --> 00:05:48,890
ryo gutangira gushora mu
guhimba ibyo bihangano.

93
00:05:49,391 --> 00:05:52,532
Ibi rero ni ibintu nk'ibyo--
ibi nibyo bituma muri rusange

94
00:05:52,532 --> 00:05:54,070
ama guverinoma yo ku isi

95
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:57,652
yemera akanasigasira umutungo
kamere w'ubwenge

96
00:05:57,652 --> 00:06:00,991
zikanagira sisteme yo guhimba
udushya kugira ngo ibishyigikire.

97
00:06:01,923 --> 00:06:05,384
Reka tuganire ku kubuza abandi
kukwigana

98
00:06:05,384 --> 00:06:07,536
Ari nabyo bizwi nk'ukwikubira.

99
00:06:07,536 --> 00:06:12,083
Muri rusange mubihugu byinshi 
iyo ari wowe nyiri

100
00:06:12,083 --> 00:06:15,416
Nyiri icyintu runaka
ushobora gutuma abandi

101
00:06:15,416 --> 00:06:17,724
badakora icyintu cyawe bwakabiri cyangwa
ngo bagipirate

102
00:06:18,085 --> 00:06:21,275
Ariko, dufite kwibuka 
ko ari icyintu

103
00:06:21,275 --> 00:06:26,450
rero gifite amategeko, ushobora kugira

104
00:06:26,450 --> 00:06:28,329
kubindi bintu nabyo

105
00:06:28,329 --> 00:06:31,467
Rero ushobora kugurisha  uburenganzira bwawe kuri cyacyintu cyubwenge wakoze

106
00:06:31,467 --> 00:06:33,005
Iyo ukoze icyintu bwambere

107
00:06:33,609 --> 00:06:36,540
Hanyuma ukabona
igikorwa cy'ubwenge kuricyo

108
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:40,365
Ushobora noneho kwandika amasezerano
wemerera undi muntu kugikoresha

109
00:06:40,530 --> 00:06:44,190
Cyangwa ushobora no kugurisha uburenganzira
kuri icyo cyintu wakoze kuwundi muntu

110
00:06:44,488 --> 00:06:48,643
Iyo wanditse amasezerano yemerera
undi muntu gukoresha ikoranabuhanga

111
00:06:48,643 --> 00:06:51,912
cyangwa icyintu cyawe wikoreye, tubyita
kwemeranya kuruhushya

112
00:06:51,912 --> 00:06:54,187
ariko kwemeranya kuruhushya
 nibyo gutekereza

113
00:06:54,187 --> 00:06:58,257
kumasezerano aba kugikorwa cyawe cy'ubwenge

114
00:06:58,606 --> 00:07:03,112
Ubusanzwe bizamo icyo twita
gutanga ikoranabuhanga

115
00:07:03,112 --> 00:07:07,793
cyangwa uburenganzira mugukoresha  icyintu
agafata amafaranga

116
00:07:07,793 --> 00:07:10,086
arinabyo byitwa ubukire
 bwishyuwe uwahanze ikintu

117
00:07:11,066 --> 00:07:13,037
Ariko aho hagomba kubamo andi masezerano

118
00:07:13,037 --> 00:07:16,534
Icyintu cyose washyira mumasezerano
ushobora kugishyira mukwemeranya kuruhushya

119
00:07:16,534 --> 00:07:19,743
Rero ushobora gutekereza
kumasezerano yoroshye

120
00:07:19,743 --> 00:07:21,370
cyangwa kubwumvikane bwuruhushya

121
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:28,025
Nkuko nguha amafaranga noneho ukampa
uburenganzira bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga ryawe

122
00:07:29,334 --> 00:07:32,681
Ariko kurundi ruhande, ushobora nanone kuvuga
ndaguha amafaranga

123
00:07:32,681 --> 00:07:35,364
noneho umpe uburenganzira
bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga ryawe

124
00:07:35,364 --> 00:07:38,085
hanyuma noneho ningurisha igicuruzwa
aricyo gicuruzwa cyawe

125
00:07:38,085 --> 00:07:44,443
cyagiye mucyanjye, noneho ngiye
kukwishyura 5 kwijana kibyo nagurishije

126
00:07:44,443 --> 00:07:48,436
 kugicuruzwa cyanjye nkinyishyu

127
00:07:48,436 --> 00:07:51,213
Yego rero hanyuma ushobora kugira
nikintu kinakomeye cyane

128
00:07:51,213 --> 00:07:56,217
Ushobora kuvuga uti nzaguha
 amafaranga runaka

129
00:07:56,668 --> 00:07:59,869
Nongeyeho andi mafaranga
agendeye kugiciro cyamavuta kuri uwo munsi

130
00:07:59,869 --> 00:08:03,770
kandi ko twegereye noneho ukandeka
nkakoresha ikoranabuhanga ryawe

131
00:08:03,770 --> 00:08:07,521
Hanyuma noneho nkaguha inyishyu
igendeye kugice

132
00:08:07,521 --> 00:08:13,327
ku ijanisha ryibyo nagurishije
kandi kugice kubindi

133
00:08:13,327 --> 00:08:17,627
ihindagurika ry'umutungo
uhabwa agaciro kumunsi runaka

134
00:08:17,627 --> 00:08:19,226
Usanga mubyukuri
bitanga amafaranga kuri wowe

135
00:08:19,226 --> 00:08:21,157
Rero hari ibintu bikomeye ahongaho byinshi

136
00:08:21,157 --> 00:08:25,544
Wowe gusa tekereza ubwumvikane bwuruhushya
nkamasezerano yandi asanzwe

137
00:08:25,544 --> 00:08:32,017
agufasha gukodesha cyangwa afasha 
umuntu gukoresha icyintu cyawe wahanze

138
00:08:32,017 --> 00:08:36,601
Kandi iyo batagifite ushobora
kubahagarika mukugikora

139
00:08:37,167 --> 00:08:40,277
Yego, rero reka duce
 mubwoko  bune buzwi cyane

140
00:08:40,277 --> 00:08:44,969
 bw'ibikorwa byubwenge
tubisobanure, tunatange ingero

141
00:08:44,969 --> 00:08:48,929
Hanyuma noneho tuvuge kubyiza
no kubibi byaburibwoko

142
00:08:49,123 --> 00:08:51,228
Icyambere ni ibanga ry'ubucuruzi

143
00:08:51,228 --> 00:08:56,072
Ibanga ry'ubucuruzi ni igihe ufata 
amakuru y'agaciro ajyanye n'umushinga wawe

144
00:08:56,470 --> 00:08:59,146
noneho ukayagira ibanga

145
00:09:00,304 --> 00:09:02,794
Urabizi ko ibyo bishobora gukorwa

146
00:09:02,794 --> 00:09:06,654
Bishobora kuba uburyo waciyemo bwo 
gukora icyintu runaka

147
00:09:06,654 --> 00:09:10,418
Bishobora kuba ari isoko y'uburyo
wakoze porogaramu

148
00:09:10,575 --> 00:09:13,991
Ibyo ni ibintu biri rusange 
ariko bitazwi na buriwese

149
00:09:13,991 --> 00:09:16,541
ubona igicuruzwa cyawe
cyangwa agakoresha icyo gicuruzwa

150
00:09:16,541 --> 00:09:19,122
Ntago bazi uko ugera hariya

151
00:09:19,122 --> 00:09:22,783
Rero niba wafata icyo cyintu
ukacyigira ibanga

152
00:09:22,783 --> 00:09:26,173
Ubwo rero ufitemo
inyungu zo guhatana

153
00:09:26,173 --> 00:09:29,971
Muburyo bwo kubishyira hanze
ntago ari ukuba bitashyirwa hanze gusa

154
00:09:29,971 --> 00:09:35,860
ahubwo ugomba gushyira imbaraga
mukubigira ibanga

155
00:09:36,730 --> 00:09:39,842
Ibyo bisobanuye ko ugomba kubwira
umukozi wese ufite

156
00:09:39,842 --> 00:09:41,502
ko ari ibanga

157
00:09:41,502 --> 00:09:45,561
Ntago wabwira ibi uwo ariwewese
mugihe runaka

158
00:09:45,561 --> 00:09:51,532
Abantu bamwe na  bamwe bajya kure
mukudashyira hanze ibice byose byibanga

159
00:09:51,532 --> 00:09:55,623
Kuburyo umuntu umwe
afite uburenganzira ku ibanga ryose

160
00:09:58,346 --> 00:10:03,546
Murwego rwamasezerano, igihe ibi byamara ni
upfa kuba ubikomeza kubigira ibanga

161
00:10:03,927 --> 00:10:06,505
Hanyuma ukabona inyungu mu ihangana

162
00:10:08,027 --> 00:10:13,505
Mu bijyanye n'umwihariko,
ushobora kurega abantu

163
00:10:13,505 --> 00:10:17,961
ko bibye ibanga ry'ubucurizi ryawe
cyangwa barimenyekanishije

164
00:10:17,961 --> 00:10:19,552
Mubihe runaka

165
00:10:19,552 --> 00:10:22,141
Nubwira abakozi bawe icyongicyo

166
00:10:22,141 --> 00:10:24,723
Iryo ni ibanga kandi ntago bemerewe
kubwira umuntu runaka

167
00:10:24,723 --> 00:10:26,732
Hanyuma rero bagahindukirira
bakabibwira umuntu

168
00:10:26,732 --> 00:10:29,891
Noneho uwo muntu agatangira gushyira
ibanga ryawe mubicuruzwa bye

169
00:10:29,891 --> 00:10:34,851
nyuma ushobora kurega umukozi 
ko yamennye iryo banga

170
00:10:34,851 --> 00:10:38,664
Kandi ushobora kurega uwo muhanganye

171
00:10:38,664 --> 00:10:44,025
kubera kubona amafaranga mu ibanga ryawe yakwibye

172
00:10:44,025 --> 00:10:46,247
Rero hari igice cyabyo

173
00:10:46,247 --> 00:10:50,053
Kurundi ruhande, iyo hari itangwa 
ryamakuru kubera kutabimenya

174
00:10:50,053 --> 00:10:54,009
Urabizi ufite uburyo ukoramo
 ibintu bw'ibanga hanyuma ubyanditse ahantu

175
00:10:54,009 --> 00:10:55,856
Hanyuma ukabisiga ahantu runaka

176
00:10:55,856 --> 00:10:58,224
Noneho undi muntu arabifashe
akabona bwaburyo bwibanga ukoresha

177
00:10:58,224 --> 00:11:01,012
Ibyo ni ibintu bibi kuri wowe

178
00:11:01,012 --> 00:11:03,388
Utanze ibanga ryawe 
utabizi

179
00:11:03,388 --> 00:11:07,942
kandi umuntu runaka yahindukira
akabisakaza kuri urwo rwego

180
00:11:08,732 --> 00:11:14,241
Iki nikintu cyingenzi
cyangwa reka tuvuge ubwoko buzwi cyane

181
00:11:14,241 --> 00:11:15,697
Bwigikorwa cy'ubwenge

182
00:11:15,697 --> 00:11:17,330
Twakoze ubushakashatsi bwinshi kuri icyi cyintu

183
00:11:17,372 --> 00:11:20,323
