00:22:52,828 --> 00:22:56,891
ariko atari ukwiyandikisha kwemewe
ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byemera kwiyandikisha

373
00:22:56,891 --> 00:23:00,550
kuri ubwo burenganzira nkuko bakora 
ibirango by'ubucuruzi

374
00:23:00,808 --> 00:23:05,808
Ibibi byabyo ni uko ufite
kwibuka icyo barimo barinda

375
00:23:05,808 --> 00:23:11,505
nukugaragara kwigitekerezo cyawe
wamaze gukora

376
00:23:11,505 --> 00:23:13,507
ntago ari igitekerezo ubwacyo

377
00:23:13,507 --> 00:23:15,211
ntago bitekerezo birindwa

378
00:23:15,211 --> 00:23:18,539
ntago wahagarika umuntu mukugihindura
kongera kwandika ibyo wakoze

379
00:23:18,539 --> 00:23:21,062
ntago wahagarika abantu
mugukora ibjya gusa nibyawe

380
00:23:21,062 --> 00:23:25,277
bizaba ari ibintu bitapfa gukunda
ahari ndafoye

381
00:23:25,277 --> 00:23:29,081
kandi ibyo uzatanga ngo byemerwe namategeko
bizaba ari byinshi

382
00:23:29,363 --> 00:23:31,521
niba ukeneye gukurikirana umuntu
murukiko

383
00:23:31,521 --> 00:23:34,748
bizarangira utakaje amafaranga menshi

384
00:23:34,748 --> 00:23:37,610
kandi nanone igihe cyabayobozi bo hejuru

385
00:23:37,610 --> 00:23:42,827
gifite agaciro
kandi niba bicara murukiko iminsi yose

386
00:23:42,827 --> 00:23:45,770
mvuze muri rusange,
ntago ari ikintu cyiza

387
00:23:45,770 --> 00:23:47,870
rero hari ibyo byari murimake

388
00:23:47,870 --> 00:23:49,847
ubwoko bwibkorwa by'ubwenge

389
00:23:49,847 --> 00:23:52,099
niyihe ntego
y'ibikorwa by'ubwenge

390
00:23:52,099 --> 00:23:56,342
ndetse tugiye gukoresha ibyo
mugutekereza neza kubushobozi

391
00:23:56,342 --> 00:23:59,730
no kubona amafaranga mudushya twawe

